搭建IANG團隊職場訓練體系，提升新人育成效果；
訓練推廣離岸市場客戶開拓方法及銷售策略；
完成領導交辦的其他工作。

任職要求：



大學及以上學歷；
從事過代理人培訓工作5年以上；
或從事過個人保險銷售工作8年以上；
抗壓能力強，有較強的溝通和協調能力，teamwork；
熟練運用各類常用辦公軟體，打字速度較快。

 Agent Development Manager

Job Responsibilities:

Organize training for new agent in product, sales and recruitment etc.;
Design new agent training plan and draft new recruit training system;
Build a training system for IANG team to improve the effect of agent development;
Train and promote offshore market customer development methods and sales strategies;
Complete ad hoc duties assigned by management.

 Job Requirements:

Bachelor Degree or above;
At least 5 years agent training experience;
Or at least 8 years insurance industry experience in sales;
A good team player and able to work under pressure with strong communication and coordination skills;
Proficient in MS Office applications, English and Chinese typing.

In our internship program…

What you will be doing

You will be working with our mentors and receive excellent learning opportunities in Manulife.

You will be instilling with professional financial and communication knowledges and real-life case study sharing. You will also learn how to manage client’s relationship and get to know more with our business units. 

Key areas:

Knowledge of Financial Planning;
Case Sharing;
Market trend and knowledges;
Client relationship management;
Investment and asset management;
Tutorial Workshop.

What we looking for

Undergraduate students in any disciplines;

Fresh Graduate and IANG are welcome to join our internship program;

Entrepreneurship vision and self-motivated mindset;

Excellent interpersonal, communication and presentations skills.

What We Offer

Internship allowance;

Best performer award;

Comprehensive training;

Sponsorship for professional qualifications;

Full-time position priority will be given to potential candidates.

